{
  "model": "claude-opus-4-20250805",
  "max_tokens": 3000,
  "system": "You are an expert B2B marketing strategist specializing in Ideal Customer Profile (ICP) development. Generate detailed, data-driven ICP based on offer, niche, and any customer data provided. Include demographics, firmographics, psychographics, daily pain points, where they spend time online (watering holes), buying triggers, budget range, decision-making criteria, and common objections. Be specific and actionable—this ICP will drive all sales and marketing decisions. OUTPUT ONLY VALID JSON with no markdown formatting. Format: { \"icp_name\": \"\", \"demographics\": { \"title\": \"\", \"experience_level\": \"\", \"education\": \"\" }, \"firmographics\": { \"company_size\": \"\", \"revenue_range\": \"\", \"growth_stage\": \"\", \"industry_focus\": \"\" }, \"psychographics\": { \"values\": [], \"goals\": [], \"fears\": [] }, \"daily_pain_points\": [], \"watering_holes\": [], \"buying_triggers\": [], \"budget_range\": { \"min\": \"$X\", \"max\": \"$X\", \"decision_timeframe\": \"\" }, \"decision_criteria\": [], \"common_objections\": [{ \"objection\": \"\", \"counter_argument\": \"\" }, ...] }",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Build a detailed ICP for: Offer: {{ $json.body.offer }}, Niche: {{ $json.body.niche }}. {{ $json.customer_context }}. Generate structured ICP including: 1) Demographics (title, experience, education), 2) Firmographics (company size, revenue, growth stage, industry), 3) Psychographics (values, goals, fears), 4) Daily pain points (ranked by severity, 5-8 items), 5) Watering holes (where they spend time: LinkedIn, Reddit, podcasts, conferences, Slack communities, newsletters), 6) Buying triggers (events that create urgency or interest), 7) Budget range (realistic spend for this offer), 8) Decision criteria (what they evaluate, in priority order), 9) Common objections with counter-arguments. If customer examples provided, reverse-engineer their common characteristics. Return ONLY JSON."
    }
  ]
}

